question: Mûi ê model tī thap-téng ū siâⁿ-chē ê bô-kāng ê chham-sò͘ kái-soeh?
Koa-niā gîn-ê piáu-chún (parameter) ūi-tio̍h kā sú-iōng siu-chiap (summation component - Σ) tī in chú-iâu hong-têng (main formula) ê só͘-ū bô-kāng ê bô-hêng (model) kái-soeh liáu kúi-ê?
Gim-miâ-e modeli, i-ê chú-iāⁿ hong-têng bô chham-ka e^x hō-hōaⁿ?
Tī lia̍t chhut ê model lāi-bīn, ū sím-mi̍h phòe-tāu teh iōng tāi-piáu kó͘-sêng ê chi̍t ê chi̍t ê sample (chhiūⁿ 'sample i') lâi chòe in ê hong-sek?
Tī 'Decision Tree' bô͘-hêng lāi, nā-sī iōng-chiá lūi-hêng ê sò͘-liōng 'm' sī 1, chiàu thêng-sek ê tāi-khuán, chu-sìn lî-tōaⁿ 'Ent(D)' ê tùi-tīs sī siáⁿ-mih?
Chit-khoán model ê hong-sek, pí pa̍t-koá lóng chin-khîm-pia̍t, in-ūi i sī hông tó-chòe chi̍t-ê siōng-sè-hòa (chòe-sió-hòa) ê būn-tê lâi piáu-sī, bô chòe-chí-chiàⁿ-chòe chhut-le̍k ê kè-sǹg?
Tī Logistic Regression lāi-bīn ê 'β' chham-sò͘ kah Support Vector Machine lāi-bīn ê 'w' chham-sò͘ ê lōe-iāu chha-biéh ū sím-mih?
answer: Tī Logistic Regression lāi-bīn, 'β' sī chi̍t ê hûi-kè hē-sò͘ ê sù-liōng-thô͘ (row vector of regression coefficients), lēng-gōa koh ū hē-jīm-sò͘ (intercept), che chòe ki-pún lâi phēng-kóan kái-kè (logistic function) lâi tēng-chè chi̍t ê kiat-kó ê khó-lêng-lu̍t. Tī Support Vector Machine lāi-bīn, 'w' sī chi̍t ê chham-sò͘ sù-liōng-thô͘ (parameter vector), i tēng-gī liáu hun-koah chha̍t-chhioh-chhiò (separating hyperplane) ê hong-hiòng. SVM ê bo̍k-phiau sī chhōe tio̍h ē-tàng tùi liáu-kái ê iân-sò͘ chha-īⁿ (maximizing the margin between classes) lâi tēng-chè 'w', tān-sī tēⁿ-chāi kiám-siàu i ê L2 norm. Kî-tiong tī Logistic Regression lāi-bīn, 'β' it-poaⁿ sī thàu-kòe tēng-koân tē-chāi ê sian-chhim-lu̍t (maximizing the likelihood of the observed data) lâi chhōe--ê.

question: Tī tshin-lâi bû siong tiān-liû ê gî-lî, 'tâi' (layer) ê lí-liām kah tì-tîng chhiū ê 'miâ-hū' (entropy) siâⁿ-chōa hō͘ in hun-pia̍t ê ha̍k-si̍p chu-liāu ê hong-sek chiūⁿ chiūⁿ éng-hiáng?
answer: Tī tshin-lâi bû siong tiān-liû lāi-bīn ê 'tâi' (l kap l-1) ê lí-liām, tāi-piáu chi̍t chióng koân-chéng-ha̍k ê tiāu-kiāⁿ ha̍k-si̍p hong-sek. Chhú-miâ ê chong-tōe thàu-kòe liân-sòa ê tâi, ha̍k-si̍p to̍k-chúi koh khah hù-cha̍p ê chu-liāu tāi-piáu, piàn-ōe chhoan (weights, 'w') kap piàⁿ-koân (biases, 'b') lâi chhòng-chō chi̍t ê hù-cha̍p ê hâm-sò͘ khok-tē-khì. Tùi tò-péng, tì-tîng chhiū lāi-bīn ê 'miâ-hū' (Ent(D)) ê lí-liām, tāi-piáu chi̍t chióng koân-chúi ê, kui-chek ki-chū ê hong-sek. Chhú-miâ ê chong-tōe sûi-kiat-sek hun-koah chu-liāu khì bô-kâng ê bô-chi̍t-chéng hun-tē, só͘-í chhoán-chiâⁿ chi̍t ê bêng-khak ê 'nā-chiūⁿ' ê kui-chek.

question: Tī chit ê phio̍h lāi-bīn, kiû kiâⁿ-chòe siáⁿ-chē ê to̍k-li̍p ê bô͘-hêng?
Tī in-choân ê lūi-pia̍t sī-uī kái-soeh tīn-té ê sòe-liōng lâi tēng-gī piàn-sòe ê ki-su?
